snippet.title: Planetary Assembly Official Trailer ( Global Game Jam 2019)
snippet.description:
Home is where you unload the scraps of your journey! Larry, the alien, has lost his home planet! 

No worries though... He has the technology to compile a new home planet with the pieces of other planets!


https://globalgamejam.org/2019/games/planetary-assembly
